{"tid":1900072,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Board Game][戰棋] Warhammer Underworlds 戰鎚冥土世界","createTime":"2020-02-27T04:07:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-26T11:48:04.000Z","uid":108073,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f2a607b1fc94f286ade13d05d2697e6dd0023f8d","tid":1900072,"uid":108073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T04:07:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zUNWbJE8JzY&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;fbclid=IwAR2X7lhJFKiBszhYtB3WiTL2CePQsX0o4qmtwk06tfNxgVdMV3B9PhwPdcM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzUNWbJE8JzY%26feature%3Dyoutu.be%26fbclid%3DIwAR2X7lhJFKiBszhYtB3WiTL2CePQsX0o4qmtwk06tfNxgVdMV3B9PhwPdcM&d=gsiGAs%2Boihw6EKwg2XwNgcF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=080daf34\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zUNWbJE8JzY&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;fbclid=IwAR2X7lhJFKiBszhYtB3WiTL2CePQsX0o4qmtwk06tfNxgVdMV3B9PhwPdcM</a><br />\n<br />\n最近超粒方出左段youtube, 順手推個坑<br />\n<br />\n好玩之處<br />\n(1) 適合喜歡玩實體對戰board game/TCG/競技性強<br />\n(2) 唔洗抽卡, 買expansion就固定齊卡 唔洗每個月要幾千幾千課金去爆箱追META<br />\n(3) 唔係剩靠牌運/骰運, 戰略走位同樣重要<br />\n(4) 多個勝利條件, 可以自己做自己野攞分又得, 殺人又得<br />\n(5) 一場只需3回合(每回合各有4次Activation) 正常30分鐘內就玩完一場<br />\n(6) 棋模型靚<br />\n<br />\n有人睇完有興趣隨便問<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://1d4chan.org/images/thumb/d/d4/StormsiresCursebreakers.jpg/581px-StormsiresCursebreakers.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1d4chan.org%2Fimages%2Fthumb%2Fd%2Fd4%2FStormsiresCursebreakers.jpg%2F581px-StormsiresCursebreakers.jpg&h=3d6ea818&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://warhammerunderworlds.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwarhammerunderworlds.com%2F&d=gsiGAs%2Boihw6EKwg2XwNgcF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=8cd0fcd6\" target=\"_blank\">https://warhammerunderworlds.com/</a>"},{"pid":"f0dfba33f18fbf226c5192553b6cbeefd409509b","tid":1900072,"uid":108073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T04:09:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bH6JFd_s17Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbH6JFd_s17Y&d=gsiGAs%2Boihw6EKwg2XwNgcF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=7a83c79a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bH6JFd_s17Y</a><br />\n延伸資料: 戰鎚冥土世界：野獸荒墳遊戲教學"},{"pid":"e72633bad8c2b5e71fc1106c4650b6f86981e3de","tid":1900072,"uid":108073,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T04:15:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.warhammer-community.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/GWPreOrder-Setp21-Board8rxfg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.warhammer-community.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2FGWPreOrder-Setp21-Board8rxfg.jpg&h=8d9445bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3df75da8487bab05bf277ef55f0f6b1204343fcc","tid":1900072,"uid":65031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T04:19:07.000Z","msg":"有無得yes yes yes?"},{"pid":"02cd793a69407ba73debc0cb7037451151ed3c87","tid":1900072,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T04:20:52.000Z","msg":"玩唔起<br />\n無咁多時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又唔想上色咁煩"},{"pid":"553b09eba8ff5be246471d1c0cd52fd518ab3473","tid":1900072,"uid":108073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02cd793a69407ba73debc0cb7037451151ed3c87","tid":1900072,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T04:20:52.000Z","msg":"玩唔起<br />\n無咁多時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又唔想上色咁煩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T04:36:33.000Z","msg":"唔同傳統warhammer<br />\n呢隻好多人都唔上色照玩"},{"pid":"252fcc96a1d7b2624022d34fc75a6b154345589e","tid":1900072,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"553b09eba8ff5be246471d1c0cd52fd518ab3473","tid":1900072,"uid":108073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02cd793a69407ba73debc0cb70374