:0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T13:57:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WUgkNmW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWUgkNmW.png&h=23c3663d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一野後追曬咁多隊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T14:26:17.000Z","msg":"貨金呢家野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"560fac29b8d31228e478057e85b6d93bf21b163d","tid":1900072,"uid":108073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"210ded3eb047e932ec49e45b4be7241ae458e9f3","tid":1900072,"uid":5281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12c46f16a4f746a2d576832d2836605ec1973b70","tid":1900072,"uid":108073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"baea5855017368d14d3ad96d3bd25ea1fa13f8c6","tid":1900072,"uid":5281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T13:36:19.000Z","msg":"啊滴頭先開左S2，我都有興趣玩戰棋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T13:51:17.000Z","msg":"呢隻算係淺坑入門，因為就算你追齊咁3季所有隊同卡都有個限額<br />\n<br />\n油棋其實冇想像中咁難<br />\n新手入門簡單油到tabletop standard已經好靚<br />\n<br />\n之後你愈睇愈想開其他深抗就另計<br />\n(本人都有玩開age of Sigmar )"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T14:25:58.000Z","msg":"呢個係underworld 可以同AOS玩？<br />\n<br />\n就係平時見AOS我冇朋友打，見滴佢玩UW好似易齊同易玩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T01:21:53.000Z","msg":"可以溝返落AOS玩<br />\n但大部份人唔會咁做, 因為性價比太低, 除非有愛/唔夠兵加落去用住先<br />\n<br />\nunderworld就門檻低, 玩得又快<br />\nAOS閒閒地都玩2粒鐘<br />\n其實都唔怕冇朋友玩既, 我都係直接上戰棋舖搵人問睇學<br />\n起到隊兵就搵人玩, 香港warhammer玩家都友善(好樂意拉你落坑)"},{"pid":"5a988bc62c8fea549472a1eaf5d32a0ababef540","tid":1900072,"uid":19311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T01:37:57.000Z","msg":"D棋好靚 心思思想入坑同FD玩<br />\n但有冇話一開始買邊一PACK比較好個D?<br />\n另外佢應該算係LCG個d唔使重覆買 一pack就齊卡咁?"},{"pid":"2413cb269314036ac8e9babd859f3ffe165f8f3f","tid":1900072,"uid":1931